      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Dec 2022 12:00:00 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://christianmahnke.de/en/post/postcards-halle/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Another donation to an archive should have arrived by now in city archives of &lt;a href=&#34;https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Halle_%28Saale%29&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Halle an der Saale&lt;/a&gt;. It concerns three postcards, the outlets of the &lt;a href=&#34;https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pei%C3%9Fnitzinsel#Das_Gut_Gimritz&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Stadtgut Gimritz&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
